name: Holographic Consciousness
description: (GPT3) If you take a hologram and cut it in half, you still have the whole picture. You don't have to have all the pieces to have the whole. In fact, you only need one piece to have the whole. What that means is, if consciousness is a holographic reality, then we don't need to have all the pieces of the puzzle to have the whole picture. That's why when we have a transcendent experience, we suddenly see the whole picture. We see the larger reality.
